Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Hubert Humphrey obituary
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brql
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Jan 1978
Remembering former vice president Hubert Humphrey who recently died. A political life well lived. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less